source.name: 2009-2010 National Voter Registration Act of 1993 Survey
source.description: This dataset contains voter registration data for the 2010 election cycle. The dataset and corresponding report address the impact of the National Voter Registration Act of 1993 on the administration of elections for Federal office. The data and corresponding report are part of the EAC's biennial Election Administration and Voting Survey project.
